The paper deals with query answering over Datalog+/- programs, which is a topic that falls under the database (cs.DB) and logic (cs.LO) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a bottom-up query answering algorithm and optimizations, which are topics that fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
